data.description: Welcome home to Fall River Estates, a quiet community bordering Deschutes National Forest & the Fall River. This beautifully updated single level home sits on a fully fenced, flat .97 acre lot. Enter into the inviting open great room floor plan w/ warm engineered wood flooring & lots of natural light coming from the many windows. The well-appointed kitchen features a 13 ft island w/ solid quartzite countertops, Thermador appliances, solid wood cabinets w/ deep drawers, full quartzite backsplash, & tons of storage. A large room adjoining the great room w/ a floor to ceiling stone gas fireplace thats great for entertaining. The 3 bedrooms offer plenty of space for family & guests. The 2 bathrooms are updated w/ custom vanity, marble countertops, & tile floors. Outside, find multiple patios & a fire pit thats great for evening parties or morning coffee.
